  "original_title": "\u0b9c\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b86\u0bb2\u0bcb\u0b9a\u0b95\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b95 \u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9c\u0baf\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0ba9 \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bae\u0ba9\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Appointment of Ruvan Vijayavardhana as Advisor to the President",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "United National Party Vice President Ruvan Vijayawardena has been appointed as the President's Adviser on Climate Change.",
        "Currently, many people are paying attention to preventing the effects of climate change on the earth.",
        "President Ranil Wickremesinghe has given this appointment to get advice and cooperation on various projects that need to be implemented involving many sectors such as avoiding organic emissions and green house protection, implementation of renewable energy projects and building a green economy."
      ],
